{"tid":2326010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周梓樂死因研訊播放片段　黑影墜落後一分鐘另一人出現","createTime":"2020-12-15T04:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T14:10:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b91f512b102678cae4e7ffc268e733ef38227202","tid":2326010,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:09:36.000Z","msg":"科大學生周梓樂死因研訊第18日，繼續由有份調查案件的東九龍總區重案組偵緝高級警員林志強作供。<br />\n<br />\n庭上播放將軍澳廣明苑廣新閣一支閉路電視的片段，片段拍攝到尚德停車場的外觀，看到於凌晨1時01分47秒有黑影跌落停車場2樓後約1分鐘，即凌晨1時02分40秒，有一名身穿深色衫、深色短褲的男子，由停車場地下其中一個出口走出來。<br />\n<br />\n庭上亦播出停車場1樓的閉路電視片段，看到在男子步出停車前約30秒，即凌晨1時02分11秒有一名男子推開1樓的防煙門。林志強作供時說，相信這名男子推門後向下層走，憑衣服和時間推斷，相信他與其後步出停車場的男子屬同一人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565352-20201215.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565352-20201215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGHpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=84a49716\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1565352-20201215.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e375af09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1565352-20201215.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"46ccbf6a12ebb90c834bc8ac7f4682f76bbd55c5","tid":2326010,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"515c0346c16b15d906d8270aa12886771da5a617","tid":2326010,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421496a1f7b69b57728a0c84ad136cc3b5a196f7","tid":2326010,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgm